title: Ciara ft. Missy Elliot - Work [OFFICIAL FANTASY RIDE NEW SINGLE]
description:
Ciara ft. Missy Elliot - Work




TITLE: Work
ARTIST: Ciara Ft. Missy Elliot
ALBUM: Fantasy Ride (2009)
ARTWORK: Attached To Mp3
READY FOR: Ipod/Mp3 Player, Self Listening, Burning




   Work is the second international single and third general single off Ciara's Fantasy Ride. The single is to be released before Like A Surgeon. Originally, neither of these 2 songs had been planned for release, but due to popular online feedback, the original single was pushed back and Work and Like A Surgeon was released. The music video for work is currently being played all over music tvs and the single has received high airplay.
